T1  - GLOBAL SOCIOECONOMIC DISPARITIES AFFECT ACUTE KIDNEY INJURY OUTCOMES IN HOSPITALIZED PATIENTS WITH CIRRHOSIS: AN ANALYSIS OF THE INTERNATIONAL CLUB OF ASCITES GLOBAL AKI STUDY
