T1  - Association between air pollution in Lima and the high incidence of COVID-19: findings from a post hoc analysis
LA  - English
KW  - adverse event
KW  - air pollutant
KW  - air pollution
KW  - China
KW  - epidemiology
KW  - human
KW  - incidence
KW  - particulate matter
